==Zviperengo Zvehuwandu==

'''Ngatitangei nezviperengo zvehuwandu:

1 = motsi (imwe)

2 = piri (mbiri)

3 =  tatu (nhatu)

4 = ina (zvina)

5 = shanu (zvishanu)

6 = tanhatu (nhanhatu)

7 = nomwe

8 = sere

9 = pfumbamwe

10= gumi

100 = zana

1,000 = chiuru

10,000 = ''mazana akazanirana'' kana kuti ''mazazanana'' kana kuti ''gumi rezvuru''

100,000= ''zviuru zana'' kana kuti ''zana rezviuru'' (zviuruzana)

1,000,000 = ''gumi rezvuru zana'' kana kuti ''chiuru chezviuru''

Muenzaniso: 

347 = mazana matatu anemakumi mana nenomwe
31,257,698 = makumi matatu anechimwe ezviuru, zvine mazana maviri ane makumi mashanu anenomwe, ezvuru zvine mazana matanhatu anemakumi mapfumbamwe ane sere!

